{"tid":781504,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"INTEL BEAN CANYON NUC公佈價格：299美元起","createTime":"2018-08-16T02:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:32:03.000Z","uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80396bcd06e96ba9cfdd1827b3c1d8996de06672","tid":781504,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T02:50:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/home/53190/intel-bean-canyon-nuc%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%9A299%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fhome%2F53190%2Fintel-bean-canyon-nuc%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25EF%25BC%259A299%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%25E8%25B5%25B7%2F&d=mvgydw%2BwIV3EwqjE35xrrF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8bfd832e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/home/53190/intel-bean-canyon-nuc%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%9A299%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B7/</a><br />\n<br />\nIntel在北美官網正式公佈了搭載Coffee Lake低電壓處理器的新一代NUC（Bean Canyon）的價格和配置。其中搭載i3-8109U的NUC8i3BEH/NUC8i3BEK售價299美元，i5-8259U款售價399美元， i7-8559U款售價499美元。後綴BEH和BEK的區別在於，前者&ldquo;胖點&rdquo;，可擴充2.5寸硬碟，後者則只能塞入M.2 SSD。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意上述NUC僅包括電源、機殼、處理器、主機板等，記憶體和硬碟都需要自己添加。記憶體支援雙槽DDR4-2400、最大32GB，硬碟可選2.5寸SATA/SSD、M.2 2242/2280 SSD以及最大32GB的Intel Optane。<br />\n<br />\n接口方面設計一致，正面是兩個USB 3.1，一個耳麥孔，側面是記憶卡槽。背部是19V電源孔、HDMI、GigaLAN、2個USB 3.1和一個Thunderbolt 3。Thunderbolt 3可承載DP1.2或者USB 3.1 Gen2（10Gbps）數據傳輸。<br />\n<br />\n新NUC的CPU值得一說，後綴&ldquo;9&rdquo;的它們整合的是Iris Plus 655增強版核心顯示，內建128MB eDRAM，最高頻率（i7-8559U）1.2GHz，48個執行單元，支援4K 60FPS輸出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實簡單d講就係i3/i5版平價nuc, 低配既graphic係iris 655 (同macbook pro 13吋touch同級)<br />\ni5版果粒u直頭同macbook pro 13吋touch bar版本粒cpu一樣<br />\n可以打到電競game同文書, 但套kit要自己買ram同disk <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088a723d795566d2ac860dd110b7d13e24d920df","tid":781504,"uid":1751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"